reviews.text: Professional service with nice doctor and nurse and other staffs.
The staff is rude and racist. Saw them laugh at and make fun of patients that were crying out in pain. 0/10 would not recommend this hospital to anyone, even if you are dying.

I wish I can put no star instead on 1 star.

It is really unacceptable, my 8x yrs old grandma got discharged from CMC today. But the drip on her arm was not removed and bleeding very badly!

Service was very bad in 7B in Wai Shun. Most of the staff were rude, irresponsible and impatient.
My dad’s intravenous drip needle area was filled with blood. I talked to one of the staff, the second staff, and talked to them again and again, after 2 hours, one of the nurse came to tell me that another nurse was preparing needles for my dad, who would come in about an hour.
The bed was dirty.
The service in 13A was comparatively way better! As soon as the machines beeped, the nurse rushed in to check my dad. During meal time, when the nurse heard coughing, they rushed in to check my dad as well (my dad had pneumonia complication).
After 2 weeks of hospitalised, many new bed sores were found on my dad’s foot and leg.

Brought my 5 years old to the A&E and diagnosed with tibia fracture. Stayed in the pediatric ward for a day to get the cast done. Though we need to share it with another patient, IMO the ward is quite spacious especially given this is in Hong Kong. The food provided by the hospital is not good, however, given the fee per day of staying in the hospital is HK$60 (less than USD10), I would say it has been very generous that they provide food. The medical treatment is professional and the doctors and nurses are quite nice. Through conversations with their medical staff, as a parent I feel comfortable of having my girl treated here.

明愛醫院（Caritas Medical Centre，醫院管理局內部代碼：CMC）於1964年由香港明愛創立，位於香港九龍深水埗區長沙灣永康街111號，於1991年移交醫院管理局，隸屬九龍西聯網，為一所公立地區綜合性全科醫院，共有病床1,172張，為九龍西北部居民提供24小時急症服務以及全面的急性醫療服務、伸延服務、門診及外展醫療服務。明愛醫院於2008年重開護士學校。

明愛醫院乃區內唯一的公立急症全科醫院，並已啟用超過四十年。為提升醫院的設施及醫療設備，以應付不斷上升的需求，政府先後撥款共25億元以推展醫院的兩期重建計劃。第一期重建工程中所興建的新急症大樓懷信樓已於2002年落成啟用。

明愛醫院第二期重建工程中的主要建築。重建後的懷明樓將會用作醫院的新日間醫護及復康大樓。新大樓為醫院提供更多的空間和更優良的設施，提高醫院的服務質量和服務質素。
